        </p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Process Overview -->
    <section class="py-20 bg-white">
      <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
        <div class="text-center mb-16">
          <h2 class="text-3xl lg:text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">The Platform is Straightforward</h2>
          <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
            Organizations post their tech needs, verified Tech Stewards respond locally, work gets done right. 
            No complicated algorithms, no venture capital nonsense, just skilled people helping their neighbors.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
          <div class="text-center">
