              <span class="text-white text-2xl font-bold">1</span>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-4">Post Your Need</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600">
              Organizations describe their tech challenge through our simple platform. Whether it's website development, 
              network security, or data recovery, local Tech Stewards see what their community needs.
            </p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="text-center">
            <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-secondary-600 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-6">
              <span class="text-white text-2xl font-bold">2</span>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-4">Connect Locally</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600">
              Verified Tech Stewards in your area respond with their qualifications and approach. You choose who to work with 
              based on their profile, reviews, and local reputation.
            </p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="text-center">
            <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-accent-600 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-6">
              <span class="text-white text-2xl font-bold">3</span>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-4">Get It Done Right</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600">
              Work happens locally with clear communication and fair payment. The platform handles logistics while you focus 
              on building relationships that strengthen your community.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- For Different Groups -->
    <section class="py-20 bg-gray-50">
      <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
        <div class="text-center mb-16">
          <h2 class="text-3xl lg:text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">How It Works For You</h2>
        </div>

        <!-- Tabs -->
        <div class="flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-4 mb-12">
          <button class="tab-button active bg-primary-600 text-white px-6 py-3 rounded-lg font-semibold hover:bg-primary-700 transition-colors duration-200" data-tab="freelancers">
            For Tech Professionals
          </button>
          <button class="tab-button bg-white text-primary-600 border-2 border-primary-600 px-6 py-3 rounded-lg font-semibold hover:bg-primary-50 transition-colors duration-200" data-tab="nonprofits">
            For Organizations
          </button>
          <button class="tab-button bg-white text-primary-600 border-2 border-primary-600 px-6 py-3 rounded-lg font-semibold hover:bg-primary-50 transition-colors duration-200" data-tab="donors">
            For Supporters
          </button>
          <button class="tab-button bg-white text-primary-600 border-2 border-primary-600 px-6 py-3 rounded-lg font-semibold hover:bg-primary-50 transition-colors duration-200" data-tab="hubs">
            For Tech Hubs
          </button>
        </div>

        <!-- Tab Content -->
        <div id="freelancers" class="tab-content active">
          <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-center">
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-2xl lg:text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">For Tech Professionals</h3>
              <div class="space-y-6">
                <div class="flex items-start space-x-4">
                  <div class="w-8 h-8 bg-primary-600 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 mt-1">
                    <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                      <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path>
                    </svg>
                  </div>
                  <div>
                    <h4 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Apply to Become a Tech Steward</h4>
                    <p class="text-gray-600">Complete our verification process including background check, skills assessment, and community references.</p>
                  </div>
                </div>
                <div class="flex items-start space-x-4">
                  <div class="w-8 h-8 bg-primary-600 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 mt-1">
                    <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                      <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path>
                    </svg>
                  </div>
                  <div>
                    <h4 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Browse Local Opportunities</h4>
                    <p class="text-gray-600">See tech needs from nonprofits, community organizations, and neighbors in your area. Choose projects that match your skills and schedule.</p>
                  </div>
                </div>
                <div class="flex items-start space-x-4">
                  <div class="w-8 h-8 bg-primary-600 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 mt-1">
