                  </div>
                  <div>
                    <h4 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Earn Fair Wages While Making Impact</h4>
                    <p class="text-gray-600">Tech Stewards earn $25-75/hour depending on skills and project complexity. Build your local reputation and steady income stream.</p>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="mt-8">
                <a href="https://hub.maxsys.org" class="bg-primary-600 text-white px-8 py-3 rounded-lg font-semibold hover:bg-primary-700 transition-colors duration-200 inline-block">
                  Apply Now
                </a>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div>
              <img 
                src="https://images.pexels.com/photos/3183197/pexels-photo-3183197.jpeg?auto=compress&cs=tinysrgb&w=1200&h=800&fit=crop"
                alt="Tech professional helping community"
                class="rounded-2xl shadow-lg"
              />
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div id="nonprofits" class="tab-content hidden">
          <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-center">
            <div>
              <img 
                src="https://images.pexels.com/photos/6646918/pexels-photo-6646918.jpeg?auto=compress&cs=tinysrgb&w=1200&h=800&fit=crop"
                alt="Nonprofit getting tech help"
                class="rounded-2xl shadow-lg"
              />
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-2xl lg:text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">For Organizations</h3>
              <div class="space-y-6">
                <div class="flex items-start space-x-4">
                  <div class="w-8 h-8 bg-secondary-600 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 mt-1">
                    <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                      <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path>
                    </svg>
                  </div>
                  <div>
                    <h4 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Post Your Tech Challenge</h4>
                    <p class="text-gray-600">Describe what you need help withâ€”website development, network security, data recovery, or ongoing IT support.</p>
                  </div>
                </div>
                <div class="flex items-start space-x-4">
                  <div class="w-8 h-8 bg-secondary-600 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 mt-1">
                    <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                      <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path>
                    </svg>
                  </div>
                  <div>
                    <h4 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Connect with Local Experts</h4>
                    <p class="text-gray-600">Verified Tech Stewards in your community respond with their approach and qualifications. Choose who you want to work with.</p>
                  </div>
                </div>
                <div class="flex items-start space-x-4">
                  <div class="w-8 h-8 bg-secondary-600 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 mt-1">
                    <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                      <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path>
                    </svg>
                  </div>
                  <div>
                    <h4 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Get Affordable, Reliable Support</h4>
                    <p class="text-gray-600">Pay 20-40% less than remote services while getting face-to-face support from someone who understands your community's needs.</p>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="mt-8">
                <a href="https://hub.maxsys.org" class="bg-secondary-600 text-white px-8 py-3 rounded-lg font-semibold hover:bg-secondary-700 transition-colors duration-200 inline-block">
                  Post Your Need
                </a>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div id="donors" class="tab-content hidden">
          <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-center">
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-2xl lg:text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">For Supporters</h3>
              <div class="space-y-6">
                <div class="flex items-start space-x-4">
                  <div class="w-8 h-8 bg-accent-600 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 mt-1">
                    <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                      <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path>
                    </svg>
                  </div>
                  <div>
                    <h4 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Fund Community Tech Infrastructure</h4>
                    <p class="text-gray-600">Your donations help establish new Tech Hubs in underserved communities and provide subsidized services to nonprofits.</p>
                  </div>
                </div>
                <div class="flex items-start space-x-4">
                  <div class="w-8 h-8 bg-accent-600 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 mt-1">
                    <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                      <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path>
                    </svg>
                  </div>
                  <div>
                    <h4 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Support Local Economic Development</h4>
                    <p class="text-gray-600">Every dollar donated creates multiplied economic impact as Tech Stewards spend their earnings locally and build sustainable careers.</p>
                  </div>
                </div>
                <div class="flex items-start space-x-4">
                  <div class="w-8 h-8 bg-accent-600 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 mt-1">
                    <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                      <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path>
                    </svg>
                  </div>
                  <div>
                    <h4 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">See Direct Impact</h4>
                    <p class="text-gray-600">Receive regular updates on how your contributions are strengthening communities and creating opportunities for skilled professionals.</p>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="mt-8">
                <a href="/donate" class="bg-accent-600 text-white px-8 py-3 rounded-lg font-semibold hover:bg-accent-700 transition-colors duration-200 inline-block">
                  Make a Donation
                </a>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div>
              <img 
                src="https://images.pexels.com/photos/6646971/pexels-photo-6646971.jpeg?auto=compress&cs=tinysrgb&w=1200&h=800&fit=crop"
                alt="Community support and donation impact"
                class="rounded-2xl shadow-lg"
              />
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div id="hubs" class="tab-content hidden">
          <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-center">
            <div>
              <img 
                src="https://images.pexels.com/photos/3183150/pexels-photo-3183150.jpeg?auto=compress&cs=tinysrgb&w=1200&h=800&fit=crop"
                alt="Tech hub collaboration"
                class="rounded-2xl shadow-lg"
              />
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-2xl lg:text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">For Tech Hubs</h3>
              <div class="space-y-6">
                <div class="flex items-start space-x-4">
                  <div class="w-8 h-8 bg-primary-600 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 mt-1">
                    <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                      <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path>
                    </svg>
                  </div>
                  <div>
                    <h4 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Operate Semi-Independently</h4>
                    <p class="text-gray-600">Tech Hubs function like franchise operations but with a mission focus. You get training, business support, and HR tools to manage your team.</p>
                  </div>
                </div>
                <div class="flex items-start space-x-4">
                  <div class="w-8 h-8 bg-primary-600 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 mt-1">
                    <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                      <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path>
                    </svg>
                  </div>
                  <div>
                    <h4 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Build Sustainable Income</h4>
                    <p class="text-gray-600">Hub managers earn $50,000-100,000 annually while managing teams of 10-25 local Tech Stewards. Create meaningful employment in your community.</p>
                  </div>
                </div>
                <div class="flex items-start space-x-4">
                  <div class="w-8 h-8 bg-primary-600 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 mt-1">
                    <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                      <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path>
                    </svg>
                  </div>
