                    <p class="text-gray-600">When big issues hit, call in specialists from other hubs. It's distributed expertise with local accountability.</p>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="mt-8">
                <a href="https://hrm.maxsys.org" class="bg-primary-600 text-white px-8 py-3 rounded-lg font-semibold hover:bg-primary-700 transition-colors duration-200 inline-block">
                  Become a Partner
